Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.48,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\frx338\fry32\pos(974,472)\frz18.9\c&H070E0D&\3c&HC5D0D1&\shad0}秋叶原新闻社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说又发生了？ 这是连续杀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又死不了 所以一点实感都没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是反而令人更加感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经挂了多少人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候真心求放过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,销量也受到影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的圣诞节就这么泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么卫兵没有出动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫兵是这个世界还是游戏时候的治安系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能马上察觉到战斗禁止区域的战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以瞬间移动前往镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们有着从外部大幅增加身体能力的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动力甲胄 Movable Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 身为大地人的卫兵拥有超越冒险者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使其维持治安成为可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是圣诞夜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是的 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前无异常情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始前往下一个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是说随便就能找到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是什么任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说有点冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先看下他的属性确认身份 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全灭？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的公会里也都算高手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经超过十人遇害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是恩巴特奈鲁雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所属公会 职业武士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,94级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到的情报只有这点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 知道这么多却没办法行动才是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟就算被杀了 也不会就那么完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松散虽然也不是很好 不过总比混乱要好点吗……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能早点解决的话 也就再也谈不了什么安稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为也有考虑避难这个选项了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要离开秋叶原吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是紧急手段而已 暂时移居涉谷之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先这就不是我们在场的人能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 等级低的人先去避难比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点确实可以商讨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在秋叶原竟然有连续杀人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想点办法制止才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说腹黑眼镜现在在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在他自己创立的议会上连续缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…他稍微有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是为了攒钱在四处奔波呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟都腊月了 明天的圣诞节活动也是大头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.10,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)}*师走：日本对于12月的旧称
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞德里芙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.50,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)}*游戏地名，赞德里芙大河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让50级以下的人参加对地精残当的讨伐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下了这样的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是应对杀人魔采取的避难措施的借口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然本意上是如此喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不要那种特殊待遇 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们也能……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬弥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打倒杀人魔喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步不好就会死的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就有觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还能复活吗喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬弥亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为肉盾职业的心理准备如何啊喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你说那啊…… 一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,股脑冲上去直接死了是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队伍配合…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是这样喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活本身就可以说是一种特殊待遇喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你习惯了 我总觉得如果把这当作理所当然的事情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而会失去些什么喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓 今天也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an3}都到平安夜了 你们要跟我去吃个饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪……？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an2\pos(1073,710)}我来请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是些多余的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an2\pos(1013,710)}平安夜还没活动简直不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38\an2\pos(1013,710)}什么杀人鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君会生气吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能保护蕾妮希雅公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我从什么中保护她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说大地人很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她已经足够强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有保护她的资格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连去说点什么的资格都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想变强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人很强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请记住对方的实力要超过大家 甚至我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要按班行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时进行报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与主力部队的联络由荠来担任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果与目标进入交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就采用甲种阵型的拖延战术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次编队所有班都配有2个治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务只是拖延和联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么宗次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的话她已经全替我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是砍了自己人的魂淡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也可以让我上阵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想找杀人魔报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是才死过复活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗大人明明为我出头的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管自己人中谁被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗次是绝对不会原谅对方的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗大人他对什么女孩都很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是至少让我有点幻想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在圣诞节喝猪骨汤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还放了鲑鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很温柔啊 宗次他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他也不是什么善良的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是单纯的是那样的少年罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一旦生起气来就不知道会做出什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那种和恐怖只隔了一张纸的温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候如果那两个人在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能劝告宗次并影响他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只有一彦和城惠两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我想正月的时候一定能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还无法得知杀人魔的去向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在继续巡逻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了晓也很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 城前辈也多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让调查班撤下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们主力部队来包围歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾妮希雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供贽一族的堇星大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然在大半夜前来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天冒然来访真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为出了重要的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此来向蕾妮希雅大人说明和谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道卫士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险者之间好像习惯把他们称作卫兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他们对维护街区治安很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们的屯所里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套动力盔甲被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被偷走的是一名卫兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据推测是我们供贽一族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫士的动力盔甲时刻需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从都市地下筑造的巨大魔方阵中接受魔力补给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据都市不同调整也会相异
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说即使带出城也没有意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来说就是如果在城内的话 它的力量是无法比拟的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的战斗能力都能够超越冒险者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说杀人魔是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个罪行牵扯着供贽一族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我惭愧也只能得出这种结论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说大地人杀害了冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是我们管理不周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在供贽一族那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 你们不能想想办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 蕾妮希雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 停止魔力供应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动力甲胄就会失去功能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但与此同时 城市的防御魔法阵也会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法防止怪物的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再启动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能立刻再次启动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要花费以十年为单位的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能如此回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我没听到就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我听到了又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能保护蕾妮希雅公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了 真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏是现在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏挑我前赴任的这时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能再想想办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再给点优惠服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能手下留情一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去和圆桌会议商量一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会和冒险者们产生冲突吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 但是也不能一直闭口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是得说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个妖怪 为什么偏偏挑这种时候不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的时候明明出现率高得让人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉斯提殿他 去了七瀑城寨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(805,670)}Seven'sHole
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说这些！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我擅自跑了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你都听到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 吃甜的能让人安心下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 毕竟世界并没有那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人是大地人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷它的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他的目的和行踪都还不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想潜伏地应该是下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会失去战斗能力 所以并没有出城的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜查他的地方就被限定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有全部搜到 不用如人耳目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有下水道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 逮捕他的可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因为卫兵能够瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使包围了他也能够逃开…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘦小的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明肩负着重责
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一直以这样瘦小的肩膀 一直努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得烦恼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找出他来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去完成我的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我看到了你努力的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MT交换
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直继 拉住仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这边看过来 大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局长！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 勇海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明承受了不少攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HP却根本不见少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态栏也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 明明打成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫兵却还不到场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是局长没来掩护的话就真的危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 在这样狭小的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而会碍他的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交给宗次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…简直就是野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真的是…和宗大人一样的武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(898,670)}Samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天眼通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗次的口传
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据宗次说 是观察空中轨迹的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 依旧没有余裕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换作平时的话 肯定不会用刀挡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是借机反击或者避开去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:17:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加给宗次的障壁被打飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明能顶住20%HP的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个状态的话估计挺不久的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要考虑撤退了……但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果逃错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人鬼可能会转变矛头去攻击大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有宗次自己就能压住他势头的保证
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}圣诞节过后的生意该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}你还要换副职？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}唉？这么精美的礼物 真的可以收下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs38}圣诞节快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险！宗次！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠那的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极速一击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}AccelFang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是晓小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐形剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}StealthBlade
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}QuickAssault
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆发步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}GustStep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 如果没有障壁的话 就被刚才那下干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 而且 那把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒他并不等同于解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}Assassinate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我没有在此之上的技巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能点头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！荠！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在工会会馆等您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然去看同伴了？在这激战之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘算着如何牵制对手 看准时机开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知没有胜算 但还为了同伴……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这是平安夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要有点前辈的后辈的样子 送点礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 我能说的却没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神刀·狐鸦丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用心观察 侧耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈祈望 为此而不断思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不言弃 不懈锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然真的是表达不清到有点惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 口传的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还什么都没有抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明 要抓住什么了的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种的 不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在你们之间是要这么相互问候的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢 主君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幻觉城市中彷徨的晓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现在面前的 是后悔还是留在心底的旧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在迷茫 逃窜的她最终到达的月光海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着令人怀念的温暖——城惠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在死之世界中相逢的二人 各自心怀什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下话 黎明的迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇往直前吧 再一次
